Deb's new book, Missed Translations, tells the story of his trip to India to try to figure who his parents were before they got married.
Interview HighlightsOn his father leavingSo, you know, my father and I, we had a you know, we barely had a relationship growing up.
He didn't know anything about me.
On how he wronged his parentsWell, for one thing, I think that getting to know each other is a two-way street.